Tuhan Shiva '(India watak mitos)
warna hitam.

00:53:55.809 --> 00:53:57.610
Kalidas Penyair Hebat
warna hitam.

00:53:57.611 --> 00:53:59.111
Piano Itu warna hitam.

00:53:59.112 --> 00:54:00.477
Anggur warna hitam.

