Berapa banyak, tuan?

01:07:42.902 --> 01:07:43.926
Rs.20 lakhs.

01:07:45.638 --> 01:07:46.662
Rs.20 lakhs?

01:07:46.772 --> 01:07:49.641
Kami harus selamatkan projek
bernilai Rs.200 crores, bukan?

